<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.202721>
    dc:description "FIGURE 9. Adult male holotype of Theloderma palliatum sp. nov. (AMS R 173131) in preservative (A) Dorsal view, (B) ventral view, (C) lateral view of head, (D) ventral surface of right hand, and (E) ventral surface of right foot. Scale bars = 2 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/202721/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.202720>
    dc:description "FIGURE 8. Adult male holotype of Theloderma palliatum sp. nov. (AMS R 173131) in life (A) dorsolateral view, diurnal colouration, (B) dorsal view, diurnal colouration (C) ventral view, and (D) in situ with nocturnal colouration." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/202720/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.202722>
    dc:description "FIGURE 10. Habitat at type locality of Theloderma palliatum sp. nov. in Bidoup-Nui Ba National Park, Lam Dong Province, Vietnam." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/202722/files/figure.png" ;
